From f5b78e723cebb367c62428cb7a67290c10a5abaf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?=C3=98yvind=20Harboe?= <oyvind.harboe@zylin.com>
Date: Mon, 30 Mar 2026 06:08:21 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 10/40] build: 15/18 asap7 designs pass lint flow
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

All asap7 designs except cva6, riscv32i, riscv32i-mock-sram, and
swerv_wrapper now build through all stages with lint=True + mock-openroad.

Fixes:
- Parser: platform file labels use //flow:platforms/... (//flow package)
- flow/BUILD.bazel: export platform verilog/lef/lib files
- orfs.bzl: stop filtering platform paths from verilog_files and sources

Disabled designs (pre-existing config.mk issues):
- riscv32i, swerv_wrapper: need fakeram verilog in VERILOG_FILES
- riscv32i-mock-sram: hierarchical - mock .lib stubs empty
- cva6: VERILOG_INCLUDE_DIRS subdirectory includes not in sandbox

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Signed-off-by: Øyvind Harboe <oyvind.harboe@zylin.com>
---
 MODULE.bazel.lock                                        | 2 +-
 bazel/config_mk_parser.py                                | 5 +++++
 bazel/orfs.bzl                                           | 9 +++------
 flow/BUILD.bazel                                         | 7 ++++++-
 flow/designs/asap7/cva6/BUILD.bazel                      | 6 ++++--
 flow/designs/asap7/riscv32i-mock-sram/BUILD.bazel        | 6 ++++--
 .../asap7/riscv32i-mock-sram/fakeram7_256x32/BUILD.bazel | 5 +++--
 flow/designs/asap7/riscv32i/BUILD.bazel                  | 5 +++--
 flow/designs/asap7/swerv_wrapper/BUILD.bazel             | 5 +++--
 9 files changed, 32 insertions(+), 18 deletions(-)

